Comment: 0,0:42:56.09,0:43:09.06,Katana Dialogue,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Shichika Hachiretsu
Comment: 0,0:49:47.65,0:49:52.35,Katana Dialogue,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Namakura, the Slayer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:15.35,Katana Dialogue,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,The rebel: Hida Takahito.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:18.39,Katana Dialogue,Takashi,0000,0000,0000,,One of the Kyotou style.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:22.84,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.67,0:01:26.65,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where I will fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:49.67,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything that has happened was inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:07.48,Katana Dialogue,Boatman,0000,0000,0000,,Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:10.54,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see it just up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:16.87,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What business do you have on an uninhabited island?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:20.52,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,It's not uninhabited.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:23.68,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A great man of the rebellion was exiled there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:16.44,Katana Dialogue,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,After the great rebellion, Shogun Yanari, who quelled the uprising,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:19.40,Katana Dialogue,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,greatly feared the fighting style of the hero, Yasuri Mutsue,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:24.38,Katana Dialogue,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and confined him and his family to this uninhabited island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:28.29,Katana Dialogue,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty years have passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:33.33,Katana Dialogue,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and not one person has come to the island since.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:38.32,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:40.09,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Shichika?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:40.88,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:44.05,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it seems our water pot is nearly empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:46.59,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come out here dressed like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.83,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:49.03,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:51.55,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It actually feels good for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:54.44,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I'm supposed to be doing the chores today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:55.51,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:03.06,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you to stop treating me like a porcelain doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:04.90,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,I never intended to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:05.88,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:07.67,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a part of my training.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:10.83,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recall teaching you to show unnecessary kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.56,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,There, you see? Now get back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:18.00,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,There's really no point in you training anymore, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:20.17,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:25.66,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What's the reason for preserving a style that's going to die out with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:29.35,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't really thought of a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:30.91,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:34.11,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been a year since Father died.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:35.31,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it time you stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.68,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to put it that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:41.65,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I even thought of a new finishing technique last night. {hissatsu waza- sure kill technique.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:45.83,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a really cool one... too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:50.93,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, the banishment only applied to Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:54.09,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly couldn't, but if you took a boat by yourself—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:56.30,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:06:00.38,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it was too early to talk about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:06.54,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get breakfast ready, so hurry back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:07.49,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:10.97,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,As for your new finishing technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:13.71,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I'll look at it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:20.81,Katana Thoughts,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:24.82,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought about leaving someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:28.65,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is the only thing that Dad left behind, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:32.87,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to preserve it while I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:35.30,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything else, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:43.42,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:47.34,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,If Dad were here, he'd cut them down with one blow and get rid of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.07,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:11.04,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you from the mainland?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.12,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first one I've seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:17.61,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:19.08,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First time I've seen one of them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:22.79,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care that you're a stranger,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:25.36,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,nor do I care that you've come to the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:27.83,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:31.93,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,bringing a sword here is strictly forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:33.22,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.21,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.37,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:38.02,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.08,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:41.31,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I didn't make the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.44,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.27,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously by boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:48.55,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I'm particularly curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:51.82,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just been taught to do so at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:52.32,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:54.82,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,"Why did you come here," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.99,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:03.30,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Yasuri Mutsue, the sixth-generation master of the Kyotou style, lives on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:04.80,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:06.46,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,My dad died.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:08.25,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:13.63,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:19.97,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the head of the family now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:24.03,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The seventh generation master of the Kyotou style, Yasuri Shichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:27.90,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.70,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was inappropriate of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:32.30,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This concerns something that happened more than twenty years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:34.28,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I should've considered such a possibility, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:35.85,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:37.94,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a pretty nice body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:40.16,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not too hard on the eyes either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:43.20,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Passing marks, if I do say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.20,0:08:44.63,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:46.59,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:48.57,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you had business with my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:49.29,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:52.28,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,I did, but not quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:54.95,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My business is with the head of the Kyotou style.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:09:01.22,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the business I had with Master Mutsue now passes on to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:07.36,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichika, I haven't introduced myself yet, have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:08.92,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Togame.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:10.27,Katana Dialogue,Shichila,0000,0000,0000,,Togame?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.07,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a strange name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:21.44,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the strategist who oversees the shogunate army.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:24.89,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I would like to test the Kyotou style.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:33.05,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This sword is an early work of Mibu Kasamaro, one of the thirty six swordsmiths of Mt. Fuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:34.05,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Test me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:36.22,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,My words exactly!{That's exactly what I mean!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:36.84,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.72,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:42.68,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyafun! {Ok, I have to put something here. >.>; see narration below for reason.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:45.14,Katana Dialogue,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuri Shichika,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:47.35,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the strategist, Togame.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:51.14,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These two people, who shared an unfortunate fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:55.79,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,met at the beginning of the first month of the lunar year,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:58.86,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in a time when "Gyafun!" was not such an old word.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:02.21,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:12.50,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Togame the strategist, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:15.47,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first person who's ever visited this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:18.47,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so we're not exactly familiar with welcoming our guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:22.01,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,No, I apologize for coming unannounced.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:25.82,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I am Nanami, daughter of Yasuri Mutsue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:28.53,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mentioned coming to seek our father's aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:30.69,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you related to our father, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:33.47,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really related at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:34.67,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:35.70,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:39.24,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should think of me as someone who's just barging in, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:42.21,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to leave your sword with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:46.32,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bringing a sword to this island, or using one here, is prohibited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:48.62,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,A law of the Kyotou style, I assume?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:55.04,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's written that the Kyotou style is "The Style of the Null-Blade."{TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:57.80,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A secret school of swordsmanship that doesn't use a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.27,0:11:00.90,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The short moments that the style came out to daylight...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:05.85,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,were in the generations of the founder, Yasuri Kazune, and the sixth master, Yasuri Mutsue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:09.69,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The most powerful assassination style,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:11.58,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(1230,1898,\c&HF7F7F7&\3c&HF7F7F7&\4c&HF7F7F7&)\}seen only in the chaos of battle during the civil war and the rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:18.94,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the seventh generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:19.82,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Togame,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:23.32,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you swung your sword at my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:27.85,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to get a quick glance at the basics of the Kyotou style.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:30.37,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I really shouldn't do things that aren't of my expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.46,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a strategist, not a swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:34.84,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask me, you weren't half bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:37.46,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,I practiced that part numerous times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:39.63,Katana Thoughts,Nanami/Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,You should've practiced swinging it, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:41.68,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,A rather violent method, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:45.72,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,I don't blame you for thinking that way, but you had to pass my test.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:50.49,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard of the name Yasuri Mutsue before, but I've never seen his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:52.57,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been unfortunate to get the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:57.49,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Using a technique from the Kyotou style would have provided conclusive identification.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:12:01.35,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,So it would've made no difference whether it was Mutsue or Shichika?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:03.36,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, would you like to test him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.17,0:12:07.83,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Consider yourself lucky for tripping over that rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:11.25,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had managed to hit Shichika with your blade,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:13.83,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,your injury would've been much heavier than the bump on your forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.26,0:12:15.25,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:18.85,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll accept your word as evidence that you are of the Kytou style.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:21.22,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:24.80,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll hear what you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.04,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:28.12,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever thought about taking over the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:28.56,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:30.01,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:33.35,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural for anyone who's born in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:35.61,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no shame in having strong desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:39.36,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can really deny the rebels their way of thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:44.73,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really look at it, even the shogunate was originally a family that usurped its previous lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.73,0:12:46.49,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And so... what?! You haven't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:47.31,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:50.00,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:51.16,Katana Thoughts,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:52.70,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Togame...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:56.43,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, being raised on the island has taught us nothing on the ways of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:13:00.10,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I suggest you get straight to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:01.87,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.87,0:13:05.59,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'd like to ask if you could leave us for a moment, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:07.09,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:09.40,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two reasons why.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:12.49,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First, the Kyotou style is passed down through blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:17.53,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you were talking to my dad, he would've had us both present.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:20.86,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The other reason is that I'm not good at thinking about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:21.86,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:24.21,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not good at thinking about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:27.77,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll ask of discretion from you and tell you why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:30.08,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard of the swordsmith, Shikizaki Kiki, right?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:30.94,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:32.44,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:35.22,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even living on an island way out here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:39.49,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there shouldn't be any swordsmen who doesn't know his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:41.77,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the Kyotou style doesn't use swords,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:44.30,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikizaki could be viewed as your greatest foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:45.63,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah! Yeah!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:46.59,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! You haven't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:49.64,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,No, but I gather that he's some kind of a great person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:51.89,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Shikizaki Kiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:55.62,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, he was a famous swordsmith of the civil war era.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.62,0:13:57.81,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you know about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:02.94,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,All I've heard was that the founder of the Kyotou style had a slight connection with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:08.98,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Shikizaki didn't belong to any school and was proud of his isolation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:11.53,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a swordsmith, he was the most heretical of heretics.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:16.20,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was a swordsmith who was said to have controlled the civil war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:17.93,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Controlled the civil war?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:20.52,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:23.70,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't affiliated with any country or clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:27.25,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and sold his swords to whomever he wanted to, without integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:30.80,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In all, throughout the twenty five countries, he made a thousand swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.64,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,A thousand swords? That's a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:33.81,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:36.64,Katana Dialogue,Shichiki,0000,0000,0000,,Not really a lot, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:41.12,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,The country that had the most Shikizaki swords won the most battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:43.94,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how he controlled the civil war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:46.41,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it the other way around?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:49.94,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the winning countries were larger,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:52.82,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they were able to obtain more of his weapons, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:56.37,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,That's a practical way of looking at it, certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:15:00.54,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the more fantastic explanation is also true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:07.00,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,150 years ago, a former shogun became obsessed with that illusion after taking over the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:11.01,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and was able to gather 507 blades — more than half of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.18,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,How childish...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:17.54,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, the shogun's new government, which had blind faith in Shikizaki's swords,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:20.33,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,issued corrupt decrees for a sword hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:23.02,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,He said it was to create the Great Buddha, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:25.07,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,That was the official reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:28.49,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the real reason was to collect all the swordsmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:30.49,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,No, his real objective was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:33.24,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,to collect all the swords created by Shikizaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:34.72,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:36.90,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,That's a rather shocking story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:41.41,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, more than 100,000 swords were gathered and brought before the former shogun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:43.88,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,100,000 swords... that's not a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:45.04,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:48.59,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a lot, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:52.93,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, was he able to gather all of Shikizaki's swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:56.39,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,No, in the end, the former shogun gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:57.22,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:16:01.79,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,He was able to determine the locations of a thousand swords...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:03.49,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but only their locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:05.56,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Then he must've gotten them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:07.57,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He had the authority of the shogunate, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:11.61,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,That only covers the ones that were publicly known.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:17.17,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The last twelve of those thousand swords were unique limited editions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.17,0:16:22.58,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The first 988 swords Shikizaki created were just practice to make the final twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:24.11,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we believe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:25.96,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,He created a thousand swords just to make twelve?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:28.63,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds crazy, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:29.82,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna.{\fs25\3c&H000000&}\N (Planer.)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:30.96,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Namakura.{\fs25\3c&H000000&}\N (Blunt-Edge.)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:32.13,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsurugi.{\fs25\3c&H000000&}\N (Swords.)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:33.26,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hari.{\fs25\3c&H000000&}\N (Needle.)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.43,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoroi.{\fs25\3c&H000000&}\N (Armor.)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:35.59,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanazuchi. {\fs25\3c&H000000&}\N (Hammer.)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:36.76,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bita.{\fs25\3c&H000000&}\N (Helm.)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:37.93,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzashi.{\fs25\3c&H000000&}\N (Hairpin.)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:39.10,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nokogiri.{\fs25\3c&H000000&}\N (Saw.)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:40.27,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakari.{\fs25\3c&H000000&}\N (Scale.)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:41.43,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mekki.{\fs25\3c&H000000&}\N (Gilt.)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:42.76,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Juu.{\fs24\3c&H000000&}\N (Pistols.)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:49.32,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The evil nature of those swords was said to exceed any other famous or enchanted blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:52.27,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Records show that the armies sent by the former shogun to collect the swords
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:55.89,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,were wiped out in their entirety by a single blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:57.93,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:17:01.80,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why I came to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:04.39,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Master of the Kyotou style, Yasuri Shichika,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:11.17,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you to undertake the task of collecting the remaining twelve swords forged by Shikizaki Kiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:13.76,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you meant by taking over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:14.68,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. {None other.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:18.49,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that you're really going to be a conqueror or anything. {tenkabito- seems to refer to conquerers / exceptional swordsmen/generals/etc. loosly translated here as conquerer. Willing to parley for different words.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.09,0:17:22.44,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,The current shogunate has been in power for a long time, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:26.65,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,It's large enough to fend off a rebellion with brute force.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:29.81,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, with brute force.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:31.58,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:33.90,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The great rebellion was the problem, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.26,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Owari shogunate has been around for almost 150 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:40.17,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No one today knows the real horrors of the civil war era.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:44.48,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And nobody thinks of Shikizaki's swords as more than artifacts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.43,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But just think about the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:51.32,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the leader of the last rebellion {\i1}was{\r\fscx150} {\r}the owner of all twelve swords,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:53.40,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who knows what would have happened to the current shogunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:55.01,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,The shogunate is afraid of another uprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:57.05,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,So they're being extra careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:17:59.01,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,So where are the swords now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.63,0:18:05.10,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,The ones we know of are in Inaba, Izumo, Satsuma, Ezo, and Tosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:07.14,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still looking for the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:10.14,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,So you only know where half of them are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:12.44,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Give us some credit for locating half of them! {ugh... literally she says "Please say, "Good, you know where half are!". Nanami uses the ~shika nai pattern which means she is disappointed that they don't know where more swords are. Togame is saying, hey, it's a GOOD thing that we know where half of them are-- it's an accomplishment!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:13.82,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:19.40,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,If they're afraid of an uprising, shouldn't we refrain from attacking the people who have these swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:22.54,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,The shogunate simply passed down orders to do it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:24.16,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,And just how exactly do you do that?{How exactly are we supposed to do it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:26.59,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you have a strategist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:29.08,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who can move behind the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:32.83,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Um, just what is a strategist?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:35.37,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Specifically,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:41.39,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the War Campaign Overseer under the direct authority of Shogun Yanari of the Owari Shogunate,{I'm under direct authority of the War Campaign Overseer of Shogun Yanari of the Owari Shogunate.}{I'm the person who reports to the overseer of Shogun Yanari's army in the Owari shogunate.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:43.37,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Togame, the strategist!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:45.88,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:50.06,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Is that some sort of post created in the last twenty years?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:53.06,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's just a name I made up myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.19,Katana Thoughts,Nanashi/Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Self-proclaimed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:56.28,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,If you need tactics, you need a tactician.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:58.26,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need a clever strategy, you need a strategist!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:19:01.70,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Special orders require special people, and that's where I come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:06.54,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, will you help me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:11.96,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,If you claim to be a member of the shogunate,\N you really don't need someone from the Kyotou style—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:14.10,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you're going to say before you say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:16.79,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I can't hire someone motivated by wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:17.09,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:21.57,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,A ninja sent to collect the swords... betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:23.77,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,A ninja betrayed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:25.67,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Your surprise is understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.67,0:19:30.43,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Such an act only leads them to losing the trust they've gained after years and years of service.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:34.54,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, they disappeared with the sword as soon as they retrieved it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:36.88,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,along with their entire clan and the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.28,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,How awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:43.95,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,The swords are masterpieces of art that are each worth an unfathomable amount of money.{The final swords can fetch a price sufficient to buy a whole country, because they're high quality, enchanted items.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.98,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trust someone motivated by wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:47.79,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.21,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about honor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.21,0:19:52.85,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad used to tell me that a swordsman fights for honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:53.99,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Honor, you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:55.67,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,I can't ask a swordsman either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:20:01.89,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,The shogunate chose a swordsman who was the strongest and most loyal of them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:03.98,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He called himself Sabi Hakuhei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:08.18,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We sent him to retrieve Hari, the Needle, which we thought would be the hardest to retrieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:11.47,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was able to obtain it in record-breaking time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:13.59,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once he got it, he disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.59,0:20:14.15,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:16.43,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,The poison is too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:22.32,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A swordsman motivated by honor could not resist the honor of owning one of Shikizaki's swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:24.52,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,A ninja and a swordsman...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:27.67,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So now, the swords belong to people who are much stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.67,0:20:29.35,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your level of trust must be hitting rock bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:30.49,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:31.73,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:32.86,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:34.95,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you seek the Kyotou style.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:38.17,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not tempted by wealth, and we don't use a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:39.52,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:42.19,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuri Shichika, master of the Kyotou style,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:46.89,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,will you use the techniques you've studied for the sake of a thousand years of Owari shogunate history?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:49.55,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,I understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:54.45,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the fact is that you need the swords, and there's really nothing in it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:55.51,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Are you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.51,0:20:57.01,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:59.00,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But more than that, it's just a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:01.73,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not worth crossing the sea, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:06.92,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I wasn't expecting that answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:09.94,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that a strategist, who's been betrayed repeatedly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.94,0:21:14.88,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,would come waltzing to this island without a compelling reason for you to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:16.69,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,So you've already experienced the worst.{nieyu wo nomasareru- literally means "someone forced me to drink boiling water" though it actually means "to be betrayed". I think Nanami is taking this literally in the fact they boiled water to make the tea she drank.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:19.01,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,So then, what is this... reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.01,0:21:22.14,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't trust someone driven by wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:24.05,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I also can't trust someone driven by honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:27.10,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That leaves just one reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:28.51,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:30.18,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,L-Love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:33.39,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,I can trust someone driven by love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:36.05,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuri Shichika, I permit you to fall in love with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:21:58.58,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Shuriken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:22:00.30,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.30,0:22:01.54,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the house my dad built!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.06,0:22:01.54,Katana Override,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Shichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:07.53,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness. How hasty can he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.53,0:22:09.61,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,No, he did the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.61,0:22:12.75,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's best to act quickly when you're up against throwing weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.75,0:22:15.39,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's just moving on instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:16.87,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,A ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:18.39,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably a Maniwa ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:20.23,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Maniwa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:24.14,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,They're the ones who knew the value of Shikizaki's swords and betrayed us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.14,0:22:25.53,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,How many are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:26.62,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Only one, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.93,0:22:30.56,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maniwa ninjas hate working as a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.56,0:22:34.35,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why one is here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.35,0:22:36.12,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see no reason to be followed,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:37.91,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I didn't tell anyone where I was going.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:40.21,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,If there's really only one of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:44.81,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichika will probably lure him to that beach straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.81,0:22:46.71,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be awfully confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.71,0:22:48.70,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going against a Maniwa ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.70,0:22:51.77,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,A ninja can't defeat the Kyotou style.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.77,0:22:53.42,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,I'd really like to believe you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.42,0:22:58.30,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm more concerned about why a Maniwa ninja is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:00.66,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:04.66,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Togame, are you quite positive that you were not followed?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.66,0:23:07.56,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have to ask? I'm up against a ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.56,0:23:10.12,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's reason enough to be extra cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.12,0:23:13.16,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's also why I didn't tell anyone where I was going.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.21,0:23:15.95,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, how did he know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.95,0:23:19.37,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, did you come here by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:20.33,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Why ask that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.33,0:23:23.00,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:24.71,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Only by boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.20,0:23:26.80,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Did you row the boat by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.20,0:23:28.67,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.67,0:23:30.93,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My specialty is using my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:32.84,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like I have that kind of stren—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.84,0:23:34.85,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Was there a boatman?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:37.31,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.31,0:23:38.01,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.01,0:23:40.89,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy has one of Shikizaki's swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:48.78,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,You don't really think you drove me to a corner, now do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:50.25,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.25,0:23:52.91,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was leading you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.91,0:23:55.05,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.05,0:23:58.21,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've had a lot of visitors here today, so my head's a bit muddled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.21,0:24:00.40,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've picked some other day to come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.40,0:24:04.20,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?! Do you think I'd give a damn about your plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.20,0:24:09.07,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Maniwa Komori, one of the twelve heads of the Maniwa ninjas.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.07,0:24:10.71,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,The Maniwa ninjas?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.71,0:24:13.38,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I heard about a ninja just a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.38,0:24:16.14,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing about us was when your luck ran out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.14,0:24:18.98,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I could've just let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.98,0:24:23.05,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My objective was to find out what that girl knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.05,0:24:24.83,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,You were eavesdropping?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.83,0:24:25.94,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a distasteful hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.94,0:24:28.69,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,You should say it's a good hobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.42,0:24:31.24,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,So you followed Togame?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.83,0:24:34.94,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. I wouldn't do something sneaky like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.94,0:24:36.35,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We came together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.35,0:24:39.08,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I rowed the boat for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.08,0:24:40.75,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was quite a bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.75,0:24:42.93,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was being quite cocky, as if she were someone important.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.93,0:24:44.42,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't even offer to help or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.42,0:24:48.17,Katana Thoughts,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Does everyone from the mainland talk this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.17,0:24:49.53,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.53,0:24:49.88,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.97,0:24:52.92,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,You're a rather dull fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.92,0:24:56.22,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose it's understandable, since you're a country bumpkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.69,0:25:02.56,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing against you, but I'm going to rip you to shreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.56,0:25:05.94,Katana Thoughts,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, this is my first fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.94,0:25:07.80,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.80,0:25:08.87,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.87,0:25:11.67,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem to have a sword, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.67,0:25:14.95,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you're one of those swordsmen who doesn't use swords, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.95,0:25:19.15,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenjutsu assumes one's opponent is using a sword, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.64,0:25:23.37,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So there are stupid styles of Kenjutsu as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.37,0:25:24.37,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.37,0:25:27.37,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that I don't really know much about fighting a ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.37,0:25:28.73,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.73,0:25:30.49,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certainly not a swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.49,0:25:33.32,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean I can't use a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.32,0:25:35.04,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And to fulfill your request,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.04,0:25:38.26,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't I use the sword I brought along with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.68,0:25:44.93,Katana Thoughts,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.14,0:25:54.19,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can a human actually do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.87,0:25:57.96,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Fear its name! Fear its sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.96,0:26:02.40,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is one of the twelve altered blades perfected by Shikizaki Kiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.40,0:26:04.16,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna, the Obstinate!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.16,0:26:07.92,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you can get a sword in your body.{TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.53,0:26:11.65,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,My nickname is "Meido no Komori," {literally: the bat from hell, but left untranslated for reasons below.}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.65,0:26:16.30,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,which means that I'm quite generous about serving up a whole lot of hell! {literally: it means my personality likes to serve (as in food) a bounty of produce from the underworld}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.70,0:26:18.30,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Komori, the maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.30,0:26:20.18,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds rather cute, in a strange sort of way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.18,0:26:23.33,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking crap already!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.33,0:26:26.17,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be worried about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.17,0:26:29.97,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is one of those Shikizaki swords that girl told you about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.63,0:26:32.82,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Don't you have anything to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.64,0:26:36.23,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really take it when it's all covered in spit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.23,0:26:36.94,Katana Dialogue,Koumori,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.94,0:26:38.23,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,It's worth a lot, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.23,0:26:40.24,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Should you really be walking around with it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.58,0:26:42.14,Katana Dialogue,Koumori,0000,0000,0000,,Quite the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.14,0:26:46.54,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no better way to keep something as valuable as this safe and close to you at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.17,0:26:50.00,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, this baby here's got a certain charm about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.00,0:26:53.85,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl dared to call it a poison, but it's far more like a fine sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.85,0:26:56.01,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just having it makes me want to slice people up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.09,0:26:58.76,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleave of Retribution! {houfuku zettou, in JP. houfuku- retribution. zettou, explained earlier.}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.20,0:27:08.73,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotou style, first stance: Lily of the Valley. {JP: suzuran}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.06,0:27:11.73,Katana Dialogue,Koumori,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.80,0:27:17.36,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Cleave of Retribution!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.36,0:27:19.49,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotou style: Chrysanthemum! {JP: kiku}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.61,0:27:22.86,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.82,0:27:25.16,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You could see me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.16,0:27:26.58,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,You make too much noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.15,0:27:31.85,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,I should thank you, Kyotou style master.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.85,0:27:35.22,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since someone has surprised me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.22,0:27:37.34,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can use your hands and feet as swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.34,0:27:40.13,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I know your secret, I guess I could say you're a swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.51,0:27:43.84,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,I hardly compare to how surprising you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.84,0:27:45.05,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.05,0:27:47.14,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't compare to that Kanna, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.14,0:27:50.27,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Did you notice something with that last attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.27,0:27:53.09,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,That technique I used wasn't intended to disarm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.09,0:27:53.48,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.48,0:27:57.07,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kyotou style: Chrysanthemum is a technique that breaks an opponent's sword in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.99,0:28:00.09,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,That sword is definitely strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.63,0:28:05.23,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, it {\i1}is{\i0\fscx150} {\r}strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.23,0:28:07.82,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been even more bizarre if it didn't seem strange!{If it isn't strange}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.82,0:28:12.39,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This sword, Kanna the Obstinate, was created with toughness as its main characteristic.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.39,0:28:17.25,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Swords are expendable, so if you use them,\N they eventually break or bend and lose their cutting ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.25,0:28:19.59,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kanna is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.59,0:28:21.70,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It will never break or bend.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.70,0:28:24.52,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, it can cut someone down every time!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.52,0:28:25.35,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.35,0:28:30.25,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Despite this sword being a straight sword, the blade will never become dull, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.25,0:28:33.47,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't break even if an elephant stomps on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.47,0:28:35.50,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can sell this for a fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.61,0:28:41.10,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From what I've discovered, while that old geezer Shikizaki was a swordsmith,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.10,0:28:46.07,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he delved into the arts of sorcery and alchemy. {onmyodo is Japanese yin/yang sorcery.}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.07,0:28:49.12,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what other strange arts he used to forge this!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.12,0:28:52.87,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,You're strange enough, pulling a sword out of your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.87,0:28:56.33,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, what this means is...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.33,0:29:00.53,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the Kyotou style is no match for a blade forged by Shikizaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.53,0:29:03.30,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, your technique to break the sword didn't break it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.66,0:29:07.69,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the Kyotou style even goes to the length of breaking the opponent's sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.69,0:29:09.57,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! That's just amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.57,0:29:12.46,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I would've much rather been surprised from seeing you actually break the sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.46,0:29:17.86,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotou style, second stance: Daffodil!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.85,0:29:22.15,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll break that sword of yours for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.15,0:29:24.20,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.62,0:29:30.07,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do if it breaks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.07,0:29:33.03,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I give it to the shogunate like that, they'll make me commit suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.02,0:29:37.58,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even listen when people are talking to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.58,0:29:42.25,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,I never agreed to help you in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.25,0:29:44.06,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the problem here!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.06,0:29:46.09,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you actually understand the value of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.46,0:29:48.05,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.05,0:29:54.52,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I understand the value of things,\NI'd never break something this valuable!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.81,0:29:58.85,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me just say this:
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.85,0:30:00.99,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, kitty cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.99,0:30:02.83,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Maniwa Komori.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.83,0:30:04.42,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.42,0:30:06.68,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A ninja always betrays people.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.68,0:30:08.86,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We sell unfair and cowardly services, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.86,0:30:09.98,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.98,0:30:14.36,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be happy to hear your side of the story, Miss Strategist.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.36,0:30:17.21,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After I kill this guy, we can take all the time we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.21,0:30:19.34,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Shichika, kick his ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.34,0:30:22.25,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, that Kanna has really sparked my interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.25,0:30:24.51,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,No. I told you, don't break it!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.51,0:30:26.05,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.05,0:30:28.16,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have any other requests, tell me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.16,0:30:29.64,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.64,0:30:31.55,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,A-All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.55,0:30:34.17,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Use as many flashy moves as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.17,0:30:34.66,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.66,0:30:39.43,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to write a report about retrieving these swords and submit it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.43,0:30:42.52,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got cool techniques that would gain the readers' interests,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.52,0:30:45.07,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then serve me up a couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.07,0:30:48.35,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I also want to remind you not to break the sword, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.35,0:30:51.24,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, the story will end at chapter one!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.80,0:30:54.16,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter one? Are you planning to write a book?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.16,0:30:56.50,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,That might be a nice plan for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.50,0:30:58.20,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.20,0:31:00.31,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll show you some flashy moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.31,0:31:01.87,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's do this, Komori.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.87,0:31:02.50,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.60,0:31:08.09,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, sorry for making you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.45,0:31:09.68,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.68,0:31:11.68,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't plan to fight anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.05,0:31:15.02,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm not a swordsman, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.02,0:31:18.67,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to lose to you just because I was too obsessed with using this sword all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.67,0:31:21.01,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, was that a bad pun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.01,0:31:23.02,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter to me. I'll beat you either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.02,0:31:27.80,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,If I use my ninjutsu on you, you won't provide any challenge for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.80,0:31:31.42,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your experience is different. Your battle experience, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.42,0:31:33.37,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This was just an introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.37,0:31:37.04,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of it as just a bad habit of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.04,0:31:38.45,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get serious from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.45,0:31:40.16,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.16,0:31:43.42,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That blade isn't something you can taint with your saliva!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.42,0:31:45.63,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cough it up! Cough it up, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.63,0:31:49.39,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,My goodness... just shut up, kitty cat.{Oh, geez. Shut up, kitty cat.}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.39,0:31:50.75,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.75,0:31:52.72,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're more obedient than I thou—
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.22,0:32:04.15,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.39,0:32:11.30,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.82,0:32:17.28,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, that was close. Too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.28,0:32:20.33,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That punk is really something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.33,0:32:23.76,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did figure you were up to something, kitty cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.56,0:32:35.13,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.13,0:32:37.34,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you awake now?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.00,0:32:40.03,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. My plan is just beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.03,0:32:40.52,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Komori.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.52,0:32:45.49,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you have a good head on your shoulders, but you're too naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.49,0:32:48.71,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He may be ready to fight, but he's not ready for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.71,0:32:50.45,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a coward who runs away.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.45,0:32:51.38,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.38,0:32:53.50,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you babbling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.50,0:32:58.23,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When fighting a strong opponent, a smart person always has a plan, right, Miss Strategist?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.23,0:33:01.12,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,You just toy with people who are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.12,0:33:05.28,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My plans work to make weak people stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.28,0:33:07.58,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They sharpen life and soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.58,0:33:09.17,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put me on the same level as you, lowlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.17,0:33:11.90,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,A strategist is good at working with reason too,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.90,0:33:14.06,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I gotta say that line was just hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.06,0:33:14.47,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.84,0:33:16.40,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,"I permit you to fall in love with me." That one.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.40,0:33:19.16,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you really brought it on there!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.16,0:33:22.31,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You surprised me so much I unintentionally spat out my shuriken!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.74,0:33:25.08,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,That attack was unintentional?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.08,0:33:27.06,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good at dealing with embarrassing stuff, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.11,0:33:30.71,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a bittersweet feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.71,0:33:33.90,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you'd said that to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.90,0:33:37.65,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now that I've heard what I needed to, everything's in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.65,0:33:39.10,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Just kill me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.10,0:33:42.22,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act so tough, kitty cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.22,0:33:47.50,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just saying that, while deep down you're thinking of a way to get the jump on me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.85,0:33:51.35,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your insides are even more messed up than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.41,0:33:54.91,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, I don't want to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.91,0:33:58.34,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed on purpose with that shuriken attack earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.35,0:34:01.89,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,At least you know how to limit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.89,0:34:04.91,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've died if it even left a scratch on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.91,0:34:07.04,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no idea how weak I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.04,0:34:09.89,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's nothing to boast about!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.89,0:34:13.19,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When we get back, we'll torture you,\N so be sure to hold out as best you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.19,0:34:17.36,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you do have some information on where the other swords are, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.84,0:34:19.86,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you one final chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.86,0:34:23.30,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not betray the shogunate and join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.30,0:34:25.48,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a cut of the profits.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.48,0:34:26.39,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.39,0:34:28.84,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trust anyone driven by money.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.84,0:34:30.77,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,You're still mad that I betrayed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.77,0:34:33.50,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just stupid to trust a ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.50,0:34:35.17,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.01,0:34:40.81,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.81,0:34:43.74,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't actually make a good hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.74,0:34:45.56,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.56,0:34:47.16,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I change my appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.16,0:34:49.79,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I look like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.65,0:35:05.54,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that Kyotou style guy won't expect this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.54,0:35:09.25,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't completely ignorant of my abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.25,0:35:12.53,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You did order me to steal Kanna after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.06,0:35:18.67,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I've killed that Kyotou style guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.67,0:35:22.36,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll change into him and kill his sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.36,0:35:26.31,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but you'll just have to stay here a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.31,0:35:26.60,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.13,0:35:29.50,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,I betrayed you for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.50,0:35:32.62,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I hadn't, and had realized who you were from the start,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.62,0:35:34.93,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have agreed to join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.93,0:35:37.76,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I invited you to join us just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.11,0:35:41.73,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it was merely to betray you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.45,0:35:46.27,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a man in this world who would ever love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.66,0:35:52.12,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.60,0:35:59.72,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could they have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.58,0:36:03.27,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me leaving the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.08,0:36:04.99,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.06,0:36:07.60,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.19,0:36:16.65,Katana Thoughts,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,The Kyotou school is truly the worst match-up against Shikizaki's swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.65,0:36:19.78,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to make full use of this chance to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.20,0:36:22.80,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can definitely kill him. What a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.80,0:36:27.65,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Though your luck ran out the moment that girl set her eyes on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.23,0:36:29.47,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.47,0:36:34.19,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The plan is to act as if I'd been captured and barely escaped with my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.19,0:36:36.42,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,then hug him before he can say anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.42,0:36:38.37,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,and kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.67,0:36:41.17,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichika!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.76,0:36:52.18,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotou style: Peony! {JP: botan}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.88,0:36:56.31,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.82,0:36:59.85,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What went wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.85,0:37:02.49,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My disguise? No, it can't be my disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.49,0:37:03.77,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The transformation was perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.21,0:37:07.66,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I take a look, aren't you Togame?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.66,0:37:10.62,Katana Thoughts,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,He attacked without looking to see who it was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.62,0:37:11.97,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.97,0:37:14.12,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean you're actually Komori?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.17,0:37:18.79,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can't even tell who I look like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.79,0:37:23.31,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, before today, I'd never met anyone besides my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.31,0:37:24.55,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard for me to tell people apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.55,0:37:26.26,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.26,0:37:27.64,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The disguise was not the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.64,0:37:30.55,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy can't tell people apart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.55,0:37:31.83,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.83,0:37:33.98,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,If it'd been her, she'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.38,0:37:36.29,Katana Thoughts,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the talk of some bumpkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.29,0:37:37.35,Katana Thoughts,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Is he inhuman?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.74,0:37:40.93,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,She asked me to use flashy moves, but that one was kinda plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.86,0:37:42.73,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.73,0:37:45.31,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really want to be useful to this girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.31,0:37:45.57,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.57,0:37:47.82,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking if you want her to use you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.82,0:37:48.53,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Use?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.53,0:37:52.62,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,You heard her story. Didn't you think it was strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.62,0:37:56.13,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would the shogunate start looking for Shikizaki's blades now?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.13,0:37:58.92,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,I think she said because they were afraid of an uprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.30,0:38:02.72,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be a sufficient reason, if it were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.72,0:38:04.70,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, doesn't it sound a little too good to be true?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.70,0:38:06.68,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.01,0:38:11.70,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The current shogunate doesn't revere Shikizaki's swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.70,0:38:13.29,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're more practical.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.29,0:38:19.02,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This sword collecting is just a way for her to get a promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.35,0:38:21.23,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The strategist, Togame.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.23,0:38:26.90,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll do anything to achieve greater fame as the army's overseer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.90,0:38:29.77,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about this promotion thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.77,0:38:33.08,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't an overseer a pretty high rank already?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.08,0:38:36.15,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Not high enough to satisfy her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.15,0:38:37.54,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants to get to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.54,0:38:39.56,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what suspicion is?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.56,0:38:45.14,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to get your hands dirty in order to reach the top of an organization at her age.{A young girl like her won't hesitate to get her hands dirty in order to reach the top of an organization.}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.14,0:38:47.76,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Having the skills alone won't get you up that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.15,0:38:50.78,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I shivered the first time I met her,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.78,0:38:53.02,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when I saw the ambition in her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.02,0:38:56.37,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She seemed indifferent about who or what she'd have to sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.37,0:38:59.10,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was trying to use the Maniwa ninja clan as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.10,0:39:02.19,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about the Maniwa clan — a clan of ninjas feared for their skills in assassination.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.19,0:39:03.19,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.94,0:39:06.61,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just using you too, Kyotou master.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.28,0:39:09.57,Katana Thoughts,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Is this all going to end here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.57,0:39:11.53,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.95,0:39:14.24,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,So you betrayed her before she betrayed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.24,0:39:15.35,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.35,0:39:17.88,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You just can't go along with her plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.88,0:39:21.08,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think is her ultimate goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.08,0:39:23.05,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To rule next to the future shogun.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.05,0:39:23.46,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.46,0:39:25.96,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,The current shogun is old.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.96,0:39:28.00,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be long before he retires.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.00,0:39:32.82,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, who do you think will be the companion of the new, younger shogun?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.82,0:39:33.94,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See where I'm coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.94,0:39:34.85,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruling the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.85,0:39:37.50,Katana Thoughts,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,I threw away my name, my home,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.50,0:39:39.81,Katana Thoughts,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,and now I'm going to die on this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.81,0:39:43.51,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can't really blame her for that, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.51,0:39:48.45,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I'm sure it didn't feel great for you guys to be used, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.45,0:39:50.40,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,We don't really care whether we're used or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.40,0:39:52.54,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Using and being used is a fact of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.54,0:39:57.36,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, in this case the reason she used us is the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.36,0:40:01.32,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm warning you now. I'm not all that bright, so that doesn't really tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.38,0:40:07.50,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is the daughter of the Hida Takahito, the leader of the last rebellion!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.50,0:40:11.97,Katana Thoughts,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,No one can really deny the rebels their way of thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.97,0:40:15.64,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,In better times, she was the princess of a country.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.64,0:40:17.27,Katana Thoughts,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,I could already see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.27,0:40:19.56,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just within my reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.56,0:40:23.30,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is aiming for the top, no matter what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.30,0:40:25.94,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants to be the companion to the next shogun.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.94,0:40:28.12,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what that means, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.12,0:40:29.95,Katana Thoughts,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Father's beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.95,0:40:31.11,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Father's regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.11,0:40:35.82,Katana Thoughts,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,She was willing to ask her father's enemies to collect those swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.82,0:40:39.33,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,What she's plotting is clear as day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.33,0:40:40.75,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.75,0:40:43.67,Katana Thoughts,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I could avenge my father's regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.67,0:40:47.21,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,She wants revenge for the eradication of her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.04,0:40:53.37,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently she saw your family kill hers with her own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.97,0:41:02.20,Katana Thoughts,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I was out of cards to play,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.20,0:41:07.07,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I'm asking help from the person who killed my father... or his son, even!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.07,0:41:08.68,Katana Thoughts,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm her enemy's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.68,0:41:12.11,Katana Thoughts,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I shouldn't have tried to rely on the Kyotou style school.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.11,0:41:15.91,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,When she herself is like a tape worm in the shogunate from the rebel army,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.91,0:41:21.29,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who is she to tell me about betrayal and unfairness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.26,0:41:24.69,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a nice body.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.69,0:41:26.51,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use it for reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.51,0:41:30.62,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now our strength, muscle, and speed are all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.60,0:41:32.85,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.85,0:41:35.48,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your arm is hurting a bit from those shuriken before.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.48,0:41:38.39,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that means I have a slight advantage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.92,0:41:42.60,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,You should know that the scratches you gave me don't even hurt or itch anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.60,0:41:43.62,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.62,0:41:48.56,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we're evenly matched, rock to rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.56,0:41:51.33,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now my rock is a little stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.33,0:41:52.23,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.75,0:41:55.81,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone else know Togame's secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.81,0:41:56.46,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.46,0:41:59.69,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't blab such valuable information everywhere I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.69,0:42:02.54,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Then everything will be fine, once I beat you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.42,0:42:06.08,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you even that confident against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.89,0:42:11.63,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,I am the seventh generation master of the Kyotou style, Yasuri Shichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.63,0:42:12.63,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.81,0:42:16.30,Katana Dialogue,Komori,0000,0000,0000,,You think you're all that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.30,0:42:17.43,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.43,0:42:19.26,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you eat the flashiest move I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.85,0:42:21.55,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My final technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.35,0:42:25.67,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleave of Retribution!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.35,0:42:31.52,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.52,0:42:35.77,Katana Dialogue,Shichija,0000,0000,0000,,The masters of the Kyotou style have been completely inept at using swords for generations!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.77,0:42:37.95,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that we're swordsmen that don't use swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.95,0:42:39.45,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're swordsmen who can't use swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.41,0:42:42.95,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I—
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.29,0:42:45.67,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I mentioned that it was my final technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.67,0:42:49.96,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's only because I just thought of this finishing move last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.23,0:42:53.81,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This unblockable technique strikes seven times at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.81,0:42:56.09,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,shattering the opponent in eight places instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.52,0:42:57.97,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, I'll call it...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.44,0:43:11.90,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotou style: Shichika Hachiretsu! {Shichika is his name, 8 retsu is like rending 8 times.}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.82,0:43:22.57,Katana Thoughts,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,What a predicament.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.57,0:43:24.36,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I really the daughter of a military family?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.36,0:43:26.48,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I get into an even more embarrassing situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.44,0:43:31.86,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to believe that this rope won't come loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.86,0:43:34.67,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My strategies always cut through, and never break or bend!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.67,0:43:36.47,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,This is hardly a challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.60,0:43:40.76,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so this is where you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.16,0:43:46.35,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what he meant by your eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.40,0:43:51.80,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's rather glittery and pretty, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.80,0:43:57.15,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, here's the first one!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.90,0:44:02.16,Katana Thoughts,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.16,0:44:05.99,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he mean that he was just getting started?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.54,0:44:10.87,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichika, what about Komori?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.87,0:44:14.25,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I beat him up in a really cool way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.25,0:44:15.17,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.52,0:44:18.56,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.56,0:44:20.51,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take this the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.51,0:44:22.34,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing this all for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.84,0:44:29.02,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really want money, and I'm not tempted by the poison of Shikizaki's swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.02,0:44:32.83,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I really don't plan on doing squat for the shogunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.83,0:44:36.02,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just started to feel like I want to do this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.02,0:44:38.32,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,, I've decided to fall in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.59,0:45:02.42,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Togame.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.85,0:45:07.80,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted you to know that I approve of this decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.80,0:45:09.13,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.13,0:45:11.46,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.46,0:45:13.03,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.03,0:45:18.74,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But to be honest, I don't really care one way or another about your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.74,0:45:24.48,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This boy has my approval, whatever his reasons for venturing into the world might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.48,0:45:30.80,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all the training he's undergone in the twenty years since we came here,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.80,0:45:34.33,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be deeply disappointed to think that it will never amount to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.37,0:45:36.98,Katana Dialogue,Togami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you this, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.98,0:45:39.69,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not going to be an easy journey in any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.69,0:45:42.19,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's the Maniwa ninja clan, then Sabi Hakuhei,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.19,0:45:46.14,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and of course any other monsters lurking near the swords we haven't located yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.14,0:45:48.02,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They may even be ogres, or serpents.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.02,0:45:51.69,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of battle I'm taking your brother into.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.69,0:45:54.48,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You're rather kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.92,0:45:58.72,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be genuinely worried about Shichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.72,0:46:02.40,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If my brother is in your hands, I'm not worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.92,0:46:05.55,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,705)}I-I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.91,0:46:10.68,Katana Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that nice of a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.62,0:46:17.76,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuri Shichika. I have four orders to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.76,0:46:18.92,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Four? Let's hear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.49,0:46:22.35,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you the first one: Don't break any of the swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.35,0:46:24.89,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. I'll protect the swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.89,0:46:25.34,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The second?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.34,0:46:27.13,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.13,0:46:31.26,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we collect all of Shikizaki's swords, it will be meaningless if I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.26,0:46:34.41,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.41,0:46:35.02,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The third?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.49,0:46:37.43,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Protect yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.43,0:46:40.75,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't mean that I'm being considerate of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.75,0:46:44.48,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not allowed to die until we've collected all twelve swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.48,0:46:45.84,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.84,0:46:47.82,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.82,0:46:48.41,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fourth?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.08,0:46:50.32,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Protect yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.10,0:46:54.24,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is me being considerate of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.88,0:46:57.02,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.02,0:47:00.15,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be a hard journey, but you mustn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.15,0:47:01.00,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.00,0:47:02.40,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.40,0:47:03.89,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and say you'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.65,0:47:06.74,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Completely understood.{An emphatic fine. exceedingly "roger/understood/etc."}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.74,0:47:07.83,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.83,0:47:09.15,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not rush.{Don't get impatient.}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.15,0:47:11.09,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When we get to the city, I'll buy you some clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.09,0:47:12.05,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.05,0:47:13.07,Katana Dialogue,Shichika,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.07,0:47:15.81,Katana Dialogue,Togame,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Love me as much as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.86,0:47:21.13,Katana Dialogue,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,A man who knew no one, and a woman who'd lost her heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.13,0:47:24.32,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,set forth on their journey together.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.79,0:47:29.51,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The journey to gather the swords would take them to unknown places.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.45,0:47:32.90,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will they face ogres or serpents?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.74,0:47:39.25,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The story of Katanagatari for this month ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.18,0:47:45.75,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.60,0:47:49.66,Katana Dialogue,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Will she be all right when Shichika's still so weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.58,0:49:28.01,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This is the strategist Togame, War Campaign Overseer under the direct authority of Shogun Yanari of the Owari shogunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.01,0:49:30.38,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It seems like everything is going according to my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.38,0:49:31.63,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Are you doubting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.63,0:49:34.35,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}As a matter of fact, your doubt is well within my calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.35,0:49:40.14,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Now, it looks like my robust, action-packed, dramatic story is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.14,0:49:43.02,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}About that Kyotou guy, Yasuri Shichika...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.36,0:49:46.07,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how far he'll go to be my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.07,0:49:48.60,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on Katanagatari: Namakura, the Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.60,0:49:49.53,Katana Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheerio!
